_sText:
<fieldset>cs:source ( face2face by paughz (first map) )

What do you do when your face to face with destiny? Primitive man built 
unexplained monuments to immortalize their destiny. Modern man on the other 
hand faces destiny with destruction. An ancient possibly alien ruin has been 
found in the snowy capped mountains, some seek to destroy that which 
threatens their view of the world. Can they be stopped?


Mission:

Terrorist: Your leaders have called upon you to remove this blasphemy
           from the sight of the earth and all of its evidence.

Counter-
Terrorist: Prevent interruptions of the archeological site and
           see to the extraction of the relics are to go on as planned.

you decide the outcome of this conflict..
